<refentrytitle>NewInfoset</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>NewInfoset</refname>
<refpurpose>
Creates a new information set in an extensive form game
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
NewInfoset[player->EFPLAYER, actions->INTEGER] =: INFOSET 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>NewInfoset</function>
creates a new information set belonging to <parameter>player</parameter>, with
<parameter>actions</parameter> actions.  It is an error if <parameter>actions</parameter> is not
positive.  The newly created information set is returned.
</para>
</refsect1>

